	"system": {
		"description": "<p>When you choose this archetype at 3rd level, you learn to share a portion of your physical well-being with another creature. You can use a bonus action to touch a creature and grant it 1d4+1 temporary hit points. You lose a number of hit points equal to those healed but regain 1 hit point at the beginning of each of your subsequent turns, up to the amount initially lost. This psionic regeneration ends early if you fall unconscious. You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and regain all expended uses whenever you finish a long rest.</p>",
